cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper deals with learning 3D shape styles from projected feature lines, which is a problem related to computer vision (cs.CV) and computer graphics (cs.GR). The method proposed in the paper involves semi-supervised learning, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves localization of style patches, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
